<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
  <head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8" />
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
    <meta http-equiv="X-UA-Compatible" content="ie=edge" />
    <title>Thank for your application!</title>
    <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" />
    <link
      href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Source+Sans+Pro:wght@400;600;700;900&display=swap"
      rel="stylesheet"
    />
  </head>
  <body style="font-family: 'Source Sans Pro', sans-serif; color: #333">
    <div style="max-width: 775px; margin: 0 auto; background-color: #fff">
      <div
        style="
          padding: 40px 16px 70px;
          max-width: 562px;
          margin: 0 auto;
          box-sizing: border-box;
        "
      >
        <a
          href="<%= landingPageUrl %>"
          target="_blank"
          style="
            display: block;
            width: 100%;
            max-width: 170px;
            margin-bottom: 48px;
          "
        >
          <img
            alt="East west logo"
            src="<%= landingPageUrl + '/static/images/logo/east-west.png' %>"
            style="display: block; width: 100%"
          />
        </a>
        <h1
          style="
            font-weight: 900;
            font-size: 32px;
            line-height: 48px;
            margin: 0 0 18px;
          "
        >
          Thank for your application!
        </h1>

        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px">
          Dear <span style="font-weight: bold"><%= fullName %></span>,
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px">
          Thank you for reaching out to The East West Initiative. We have
          received your request with great care.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px">
          We will review the information you have provided us and get back to
          you as soon as possible.
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px">
          If you have any questions, do not hesitate to contact our support team
          at&nbsp;<a
            href="mailto:EastWest%20Support%3c<%= supportEmail %>%3e"
            target="_blank"
            style="color: #c80030; font-weight: 600; text-decoration: none"
            ><%= supportEmail %></a
          >
        </p>
        <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px">Kind regards,</p>
      </div>
      <div style="background-color: #333">
        <div
          style="
            padding: 32px 16px;
            max-width: 564px;
            margin: 0 auto;
            box-sizing: border-box;
            text-align: center;
            color: #fff;
          "
        >
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0">
            Â© 2020 The East to West Initiative Limited.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin: 0">
            Unit 3D North Point House, North Point Business Park, New Mallow
            Road, Cork. T23 AT2P, Ireland.
          </p>
          <p style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 24px; margin: 16px 0 0">
            <a
              href="<%= termsUrl %>"
              target="_blank"
              style="text-decoration: none; color: #c80030"
            >
              Terms of Use
            </a>
            &nbsp;
            <span style="color: #fff">|</span>
            &nbsp;
            <a
              href="<%= privacyUrl %>"
              target="_blank"
              style="text-decoration: none; color: #c80030"
            >
              Privacy Policy
            </a>
          </p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </body>
</html>
